# Keep the build context small and free of secrets/artefacts (the image rebuilds
# deps and the SPA itself; env comes from compose, not a baked-in file).
**/node_modules
client/dist
client/.vite
server/uploads
**/.env
.git
.github
.claude
# DB seed dumps stay out of the image; the db service bind-mounts them separately.
deploy/db-init
ios-swift
**/*.md
**/.DS_Store
